{"tid":827083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹過後 綿羊仔粉嶺公路遇塌樹翻倒　鐵騎士重創不治","createTime":"2018-09-18T16:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T01:59:34.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc5e12a4991017b30d2c983ccaae04bad92b234","tid":827083,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180919/bkn-20180919001334121-0919_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180919%2Fbkn-20180919001334121-0919_00822_001.html&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1fd5a26d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180919/bkn-20180919001334121-0919_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n路旁塌樹成馬路陷阱，鐵騎士命喪粉嶺公路！昨日（19日）晚上11時許，一名男子駕駛綿羊仔電單車，沿慢線向大埔行駛，至大窩村對開時，疑輾過路超強颱風「天竹」遺留下來的倒塌樹林，登時失平衡，人仰車翻，他連翻帶滾倒地，身體受重傷，警方接報到場調查，救護車將他送院搶救，可惜證實不治。警方仍在調查肇事原因。 <br />\n<br />\n現場所見，由於颱風過後，不少倒塌樹未及清理，粉嶺公路的慢線仍有大量樹木樹枝，形成危機處處。"},{"pid":"d703b9e231ac13d58fe5852a8e9876c26a28eb49","tid":827083,"uid":142965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46447368be0aa4311f6afd841ac71adaf22973a","tid":827083,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"自殺又想屈我地特首同局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259af7844c8e4e15ea54e1e01810dfeb94eadfe4","tid":827083,"uid":12892,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"昨日（19日）晚上11時許<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a5961edd66628a8da49034efd6f8a8f2b8664c","tid":827083,"